                  {
                    "alias": "description",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "January, 2025 (Lincoln, NE) \u2014 The Office of the CIO is pleased to announce that Joe Beer has been promoted to IT Supervisor for the Project Management Office! He was elevated to this position effective January 27th, 2025."
